title: ADA Urban 1b1b Available Soon!- Aura West
posting_body: This is a 1 Bedroom + 1 Den, 1 Bath, approximately 735 Sq.
West Seattle’s newest apartment community offers a mix of studio, one- and two-bedroom apartments, plus two-bedroom townhomes and live/work units.
To live at Aura West Seattle is to live locally inspired by West Seattle’s laid-back culture yet be actively connected to everything Seattle has to offer.

2" Window Coverings Throughout, Modern Urban Residences, Custom Carpeted Bedrooms, Private Patios or Balconies*, Kitchens Designed for the "Foodie", Custom Cabinetry with Soft-Close Doors and Drawers Offered in Two Color Schemes, Danze® Spring Pull Down Faucet, Walk-In Closets*, Wood-Style Flooring, Modern Lighting Throughout Apartment, In-Home Stacked Full-Size Washer/Dryer, Under-Mount "Farm Style" Sink, Amazing Seattle Skyline Views*, Soaring 10' Ceilings at Penthouse Level, Expansive Floor-to-Ceiling Windows in Living Spaces, Pendant Lighting Over Kitchen Bars/Islands, Whirlpool® Stainless Steel Appliances, Quartz Countertops

Package Acceptance with 24-7 Parcel Package Lockers, Multi-Level Parking Garage with Plenty of Parking for All Your Vehicles, Onsite Bike and Pet Washing Station, Social Gathering Spaces, 24-Hour Maintenance Emergency Service, WiFi in All Common Areas, Energizing Fitness Center with Cardio Theater and Free Weights, Bike Storage, Access to West Seattle Hill Climb, RapidRide Stop Right Outside Your Front Door.

One-Stop (10 minutes) to Downtown Seattle, Multi-Size Storage Lockers Available, Climate Controlled Interior Corridors, Resident Lounge and Social Gathering Area with Coffee Bar, Rooftop Pet Park, Uber-Chic Rooftop Deck, Grilling Stations, Personal Gardening Spaces
We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.
